{
  "id": "6a0954a0c450b46dc897fee5",
  "title": "Cosense以外の設計哲学",
  "created": 1778996385,
  "updated": 1779110607,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0954a0c450b46dc897fee5",
      "text": "Cosense以外の設計哲学",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778996385,
      "updated": 1778996385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0954a00000000000a60232",
      "text": " [Cosenseの哲学]でなく[Cosense以外の設計哲学]もいろいろ読みたくなった[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778996385,
      "updated": 1778998332
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0954a00000000000a60233",
      "text": "  > プログラミング言語 Ruby は、一時期「[驚き最小の原則]」とともに語られることが多かった。ただし、作者のまつもとゆきひろはこの原則を Ruby の設計哲学として採用したことはないと述べているhttps://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/驚き最小の原則",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1778996385,
      "updated": 1778996581
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0954a00000000000a60234",
      "text": "   ここで[設計哲学]という言葉が出てきた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778996385,
      "updated": 1778996385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0954a00000000000a60235",
      "text": "  こんなふうに世の中にある製品にはそれぞれ哲学があるなら、",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778996385,
      "updated": 1778998335
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0958e40000000000a60273",
      "text": "  [Cosenseの哲学]みたいな読み物が他にもたくさんあるのでは",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1778997477,
      "updated": 1778997477
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0965400000000000a46f4c",
      "text": "  例えば、こんなのでいいんですか？ [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779000641,
      "updated": 1779000674
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0964320000000000a46f47",
      "text": "   [TMTOWTDI]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779000371,
      "updated": 1779000378
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09643d0000000000a46f49",
      "text": "    [Perl]のモットーで設計哲学でもある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779000381,
      "updated": 1779000583
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0964860000000000a46f4a",
      "text": "   PEP 20 [Zen of Python]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779000455,
      "updated": 1779000610
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09648a0000000000a46f4b",
      "text": "    Zen とは[禅]のことだけど、ここでは設計哲学みたいなもん",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779000459,
      "updated": 1779000696
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0980cc0000000000640bcf",
      "text": "   です！！[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1779007693,
      "updated": 1779007765
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098dfc000000000063f097",
      "text": "   [C言語の精神]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011068,
      "updated": 1779011078
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e50000000000063f0a9",
      "text": "    C言語の設計哲学みたいなもん",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011152,
      "updated": 1779011176
    },
    {
      "id": "6a098e6c000000000063f0aa",
      "text": "    しかし、古い言語ばかりだね、新しい言語は若い人に任せた [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779011181,
      "updated": 1779011247
    },
    {
      "id": "6a097ad8000000000077560f",
      "text": "\t\t例えばボードゲーム[黙談 -Silentalk-]の場合はこんな感じ[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779006169,
      "updated": 1779006240
    },
    {
      "id": "6a097ae30000000000775610",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/silentalk/ルール逸脱可能余白]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779006180,
      "updated": 1779006185
    },
    {
      "id": "6a097ae90000000000775611",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/silentalk/たまたまその時に強い人が分け与える]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779006185,
      "updated": 1779006190
    },
    {
      "id": "6a097aee0000000000775612",
      "text": "\t\t\t[/silentalk/黙談には奉行問題自体をゲームに取り入れた]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779006190,
      "updated": 1779006196
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0964330000000000a46f48",
      "text": "   想像してなかった方面からの設計哲学でした！よい！！[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1779000372,
      "updated": 1779110607
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09cc22000000000096ff24",
      "text": "   絶対おもろいやつ[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1779026978,
      "updated": 1779026983
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09cc27000000000096ff25",
      "text": "    明日読む",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1779026984,
      "updated": 1779026986
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09cae20000000000160ee8",
